@startuml DFD_Level2_Veterinary_Appointments
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

' External Entities
actor "Pet Owner" as Owner <<External Entity>>
actor "Veterinarian/Clinic" as Vet <<External Entity>>
database "OpenStreetMap API" as OSM <<External System>>
database "Firebase FCM" as FCM <<External System>>

' Level 2 Processes for Veterinary Appointments (6.0)
rectangle "6.1\nQuery Nearby Clinics\n(GPS-based)" as QueryClinics <<Process>>
rectangle "6.2\nCalculate Distances\n(Haversine)" as CalcDistance <<Process>>
rectangle "6.3\nSort & Rank\nClinics" as SortClinics <<Process>>
rectangle "6.4\nRetrieve Available\nTime Slots" as GetSlots <<Process>>
rectangle "6.5\nCreate Appointment\nRecord" as CreateAppt <<Process>>
rectangle "6.6\nNotify Clinic\n(New Request)" as NotifyClinic <<Process>>
rectangle "6.7\nSchedule Reminders\n(24h, 2h)" as ScheduleReminders <<Process>>
rectangle "6.8\nUpdate/Cancel\nAppointment" as UpdateAppt <<Process>>

' Data Stores
database "D2: Pets" as D2 <<Data Store>>
database "D6: Appointments" as D6 <<Data Store>>
database "D7: Clinics" as D7 <<Data Store>>
database "D1: Users" as D1 <<Data Store>>

' Data Flows - Discovery Phase
Owner --> QueryClinics : GPS Location\n(lat, lng)\nPreferred Date

QueryClinics --> OSM : GPS + Radius (10km)\nCategory: veterinary_clinic
OSM --> QueryClinics : Clinic List\n(OSM IDs, names, addresses)

QueryClinics --> D7 : Match OSM IDs
D7 --> QueryClinics : Clinic Details\n(ratings, contact, services)

QueryClinics --> CalcDistance : User Location + Clinic Locations
CalcDistance --> SortClinics : Distance List
SortClinics --> Owner : Sorted Clinics by Distance\n(nearest first)

' Booking Phase
Owner --> GetSlots : Selected Clinic ID\nPreferred Date
GetSlots --> D6 : Query Existing Appointments
D6 --> GetSlots : Booked Slots
GetSlots --> D7 : Get Clinic Hours
D7 --> GetSlots : Operating Hours
GetSlots --> Owner : Available Time Slots

Owner --> CreateAppt : Selected Slot\nPet ID, Reason
CreateAppt --> D2 : Get Pet Info
D2 --> CreateAppt : Pet Details
CreateAppt --> D1 : Get Owner Info
D1 --> CreateAppt : Owner Contact

CreateAppt --> D6 : Store Appointment\n(status: Requested)
CreateAppt --> NotifyClinic : Appointment Details

NotifyClinic --> D7 : Get Clinic Contact
D7 --> NotifyClinic : Clinic FCM Token
NotifyClinic --> FCM : Notification Payload
FCM --> Vet : New Appointment Alert

CreateAppt --> ScheduleReminders : Appointment DateTime
ScheduleReminders --> D6 : Store Reminder Jobs\n(datetime - 24h, datetime - 2h)
ScheduleReminders --> Owner : Confirmation + Reminders

' Update/Cancel Phase
Owner --> UpdateAppt : Reschedule/Cancel Request
Vet --> UpdateAppt : Confirm/Reject Request
UpdateAppt --> D6 : Update Status/DateTime
UpdateAppt --> NotifyClinic : Status Change
NotifyClinic --> Owner : Update Confirmation
NotifyClinic --> Vet : Update Notification

note right of QueryClinics
  Level 2 DFD: Veterinary Appointments (6.0)
  
  Sub-processes:
  6.1 - GPS-based clinic discovery (OpenStreetMap)
  6.2 - Distance calculation (Haversine formula)
  6.3 - Clinic sorting by proximity
  6.4 - Availability query
  6.5 - Appointment creation
  6.6 - Clinic notification
  6.7 - Reminder scheduling (24h, 2h before)
  6.8 - Update/cancel handling
  
  Features:
  - 10km default radius (expandable to 50km if <3 results)
  - Real-time availability checking
  - Firebase Cloud Messaging push notifications
  - Appointment reminders: 24-hour and 2-hour intervals
  - Rescheduling: 4-hour minimum notice required
  - Haversine distance calculation for accurate sorting
  - Status lifecycle: Requested → Confirmed/Rejected → Completed/Cancelled/NoShow
end note

note bottom of D6
  Appointments table stores:
  - pet_id, owner_id, clinic_id
  - datetime, reason, status
  - created_at, updated_at
  - reminder_24h_sent, reminder_2h_sent
end note

note bottom of D7
  Clinics table stores:
  - clinic_id, osm_id, name
  - address, lat, lng, rating
  - phone, email, services
  - operating_hours, fcm_token
end note

@enduml
